Informal changelog:
Version 1: Beginning
Version 2: Removed all the crap about implicit references, changed it to
explicit but auto-referencing pointers.  Simplified the type system some.
Version 3: Removed default values, made everything default to 0 or NIL.
Version 4: Removed auto-dereferencing values
Version 5: Started the type system over from scratch, using only int and float
